### Observe (AC: QGM-013..QGM-023)
POST {{base}}/api/quantum-gomoku/games/{{gameId}}/observations
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
# Optional test-only seed header if supported
X-Test-Random-Seed: 42

{
  "playerId": "BLACK"
