### Reset (AC: QGM-028)
POST {{base}}/api/quantum-gomoku/games/{{gameId}}/reset
Accept: application/json

### Delete (AC: QGM-029)
DELETE {{base}}/api/quantum-gomoku/games/{{gameId}}
Accept: application/json
